{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_12_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 でっかいクロワッサンが！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……{user}さん……うちのこと\n追いかけて来てくれたんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… {user}-san…\nyou came after me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7014961879
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "優、すまない。この通りだ。俺が悪かった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ I’m sorry. It’s my fault…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7014961879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと、頭上げて下さい\nなんでうちに謝ってるんです……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait‚ please raise your head.\nWhy are you apologizing to me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.0774826686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺が至らないせいで、優に不快な思いをさせてしまった\n衣装の色か、デザインか？　まだ時間はあるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of my shortcomings‚ I made you uncomfortable.\nWas it the color? The design? We still have time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2050789197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います……うち、不快な思いなんてしてません\n誤解させるような態度を取ってしまって……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no… I wasn’t uncomfortable at all.\nI’m sorry for acting in a way that misled you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.4659635544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、どうして怒っているんだ？\n今だって、そんなに頬を膨らませて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why are you angry?\nEven now‚ you’re puffing out your cheeks like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "膨らませて？　……ち、違います！　これは、その……\nと、とにかく、うちは怒ってなんていませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Puffing them out? N-no! It’s not that‚ it’s just…\nA-anyway‚ I’m not angry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6281175931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあどうして……。くっ、俺はなんて役立たずなんだ\n優の気持ちを察することさえ、出来ないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why…? Ugh‚ I’m so useless.\nI can’t even understand how you feel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "役立たずやなんて、そんなことっ……！\n……あぁもう、だから違うんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t call yourself useless…!\n…Oh please‚ that’s not it at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.9701357206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ほっぺは、その、膨らませてたんやなくて……\nふ…………ふ……太ったん、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My cheeks aren’t puffed out…\nI… I’ve gained weight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2116552036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　な、なんだって？\nよく聞こえなかったから、もう一度言ってくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? W-what?\nI didn’t quite catch that. Could you say it again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.9465331714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやから！　うち！　食べ過ぎて太っただけなんです！\n……な、なんてこと言わせるんですかぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said! I! just gained weight from eating too much!\n…Why are you making me say that out loud~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.005739214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4914083481
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2666690827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと、大声で言うつもりやなかったのに……\n恥ずかしい……{user}さんのあほ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never meant to shout something like that…\nThis is so embarrassing… you dummy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666690827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、うちが自分でちゃんと痩せるまで\n構わんといて欲しかったのに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I wanted you to just leave me be\nuntil I’d properly slimmed down on my own…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9249210994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、分かったから、落ち着いてくれ\nまずは事務所に戻って、ゆっくり話さないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ okay‚ just calm down.\nLet’s go back to the office and talk it through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.6148080509
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.6148080509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "極烙拉麺さんのお仕事をいただいたあの日から\nうちの激辛対策は、パワーアップしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since I got the Gokuraku Ramen job‚\nI’ve stepped up my spicy training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1348196574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "これまでは一日一回、キムチとか麻婆豆腐とか\n辛い料理を一品食べて、徐々に慣らしてきたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before‚ once a day‚ I’d eat something spicy—\nlike kimchi or mapo tofu—to build tolerance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.2006358465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんなんじゃ甘過ぎる\nこのペースやと、イベントに間に合わんと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that was too soft.\nAt that pace‚ I wouldn’t make it in time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.3974162103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "激辛10倍カレー、ハバネロ入りトムヤムクンに\n四川風麻婆豆腐、真っ赤な辛味噌の担々麺……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ten-times-spicy curry‚ habanero tom yum‚\nSichuan mapo tofu‚ bright-red spicy miso tantanmen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "激辛料理に毎食チャレンジすることにしたんです\n辛いし痛いしで、それはもう大変でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I challenged myself with ultra-spicy food every meal.\nIt was spicy and painful—just brutal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.0617248854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことになっていたのか。俺に相談してくれれば\n……いや、相談されても何が出来たか分からないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had no idea… you could’ve told me.\n…Though I don’t know what I could’ve done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.084559409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、これはうちの挑戦ですから\nそれに体調を崩すほどの無理はしてません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this was my challenge.\nAnd I didn’t push myself to the point of getting sick.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.7333311717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでしても、激辛料理には慣れませんでした\nでもそんな中、うちは気付いてしまったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I still couldn’t get used to it.\nBut then I realized something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8666619619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
