      "text": "最高の自分で臨まんと、お客さんにも極烙拉麺さんにも\n失礼やと思うから……ですからうち、痩せてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I don’t show up as my best self‚ it’d be rude\nto the customers and Gokuraku Ramen. So I’ll slim down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.0999932607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.6666599274
    },
    {
