      "text": "無茶なダイエットは体に負担がかかる。辛い物の特訓も\nだから、無理なく出来る方法を探してみるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Extreme dieting is hard on the body—and so is spicy training.\nSo we’ll find a way you can keep it up without overdoing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.3418570385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
